    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While the engine and transmission are in decent working order, the car shows noticeable signs of its age and use. You can expect some cosmetic imperfections, such as minor dents, scratches on the exterior, and visible wear on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, it remains dependable for commuting, though it may require more frequent routine maintenance than a newer model. All essential systems like the heater and lights are functional, making this a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
