    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle with zero compromises, this is a rare find that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new car.",
