    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered like a member of the family. It drives just as smoothly as the day it rolled off the lot\u2014honestly, maybe even better! You\u2019ll find the interior is spotless and it purrs like a kitten the moment you turn the key. It\u2019s just one of those rare finds that\u2019s been loved exactly the way a car should be. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, let's chat cars, and take it for a spin!",
